desc: Stilfulle utemøbler som er vedlikeholdsfrie, møblene kan stå ute hele året! Resirkulete hagemøbler med 20 års garanti - nyt sesongen med god samvittighet.

layout.text:
Rede Furniture is a small Scandinavian brand with big, worldwide ambitions. With our green- certified outdoor furniture, made from recycled plastic we are committed in our souls to help our world be more caring without losing the element of beauty.
When you buy from us, we give back. Not only are you helping our environment, you also give to children and animals in need of a helping hand.
